{
  "stem": "58.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] On the way, we lost about three, four dozen people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Some people couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was about 22, 23 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were riding half, half-- half-tracks in the front, and half in the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were in the middle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You know, it's easier to ride a half-track than to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Nobody was used to walk 22, 23 kilometers in one day, unless you were in the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We came-- yeah, we had a watchman in the city that repaired watches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was a heavy, actually Hasidic Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he couldn't keep up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They tied him-- they tied a chain around his waist and tied him to the half track.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they tried-- he should walk, but he couldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So he fell, and that's how he died, by pulling him on the ground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They made pictures and were laughing, the Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And eventually, we came into a big ranch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They took us into a big ranch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they told us to sit down on our legs, the same way we marched to sit on floor with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they brought us some ice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because they were afraid if they give us water, we could all get sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So they brought us pieces of ice to everybody, no food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And all of a sudden we heard some firing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Light machine gun fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You know, everything was new.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I never heard in my life shooting from a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the rumors was going around that they shot four people that tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "See, everybody knew around the surroundings, 22 kilometers from the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So they shot-- four people were shot, four they brought back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They put up a gallow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we had to see them hang all of them four.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
